file.name: facet-string-length-invalid.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: OpenAPI Test
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:9999/v2
paths:
  /ping:
    post:
      summary: test
      description: test it
      operationId: pingOp
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/SomeObj'
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content: {}
components:
  schemas:
    SomeObj:
      type: string
      minLength: 1
      maxLength: 3
      example: きんぎょきんぎょ
